sections.text:
79-860.Professional practices; terms, defined.

For purposes of sections 79-859 to 79-870:

(1) Board means the State Board of Education; and

(2) Commissioner means the Commissioner of Education.

SourceLaws 1993, LB 348, § 30;R.S.1943, (1994), § 79-1280.01;Laws 1996, LB 900, § 485;Laws 2024, LB1306, § 2.
